questions.scenario:
An AWS IAM trust policy for a GitHub OIDC role contains:

```json
"Condition": {
  "StringLike": {
    "token.actions.githubusercontent.com:sub": "repo:my-org/my-repo:*"
  }
}
```

A developer forks `my-org/my-repo` to `attacker/my-repo` and tries to assume the role from a workflow in their fork. Does it work?
